title: Retro Bicycle Sound Effect Pack 01
description: This audio library contains the sounds of an old used Belorussian bicycle. The sound recordings have 2 channels: chain wheel, rear wheel and additional sounds.
longDescription:
This audio library contains the sounds of an old used Belorussian bicycle.

The sound recordings have 2 channels: chain wheel, rear wheel and additional sounds.


It always seemed that every bike had a different sound. One of my friend’s bikes was particularly interesting and older, so I decided that I would definitely record its sound. I hope that as time permits I will be able to make more such sound effect collections, because it was very interesting.


This sound effect collection is ideal for use in game software, applications, commercials, movies, TV shows,

videos, animation, and any other entertainment industry where a high-quality audio effect is essential.
technicalDetails:
Features:

  • 113 Retro bicycle sound effect.
  • For productions where old bikes appear. 

Number of Audio Waves: 113

Number of Audio Cues: 113

Sample rate / bit rate: 44,100 Hz / 16bit / Mono and Stereo files

Do Sound FX loop: One shot and loop files

Minutes of audio provided: 25min 10sec

Supported Development Platforms:

Windows: Yes

Mac: Yes
